| # | Risk | Status |
|---|---|---|
| A01 Broken Access Control | ❌ Fail | No auth/authz on PII endpoint |
| A02 Cryptographic Failures | ❌ Fail | No TLS |
| A03 Injection | ✅ Pass | No dynamic queries or eval present |
| A04 Insecure Design | ❌ Fail | No security controls designed in |
| A05 Security Misconfiguration | ❌ Fail | Default headers, default error handler |
| A06 Vulnerable Components | ⚠️ Unknown | No `npm audit` output available |
| A07 Identification & Auth Failures | ❌ Fail | No authentication at all |
| A09 Logging & Monitoring Failures | ❌ Fail | No logging or audit trail |
| API2 Broken Authentication | ❌ Fail | — |
| API3 Broken Object Property Level Auth | ❌ Fail | Full user objects returned |
| API4 Unrestricted Resource Consumption | ❌ Fail | No rate limiting or pagination |
